# Romanovo, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Romanovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kabansky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 131 as of 2010. There are 17 streets.
Geography
Romanovo is located 39&nbsp;km north of Kabansk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Khandala is the nearest rural locality.
